  "texts": [
    "These models utilize neural networks to autonomously discern intricate patterns and relationships within text data (Zhao et al. 2023).",
    "Their capacity to automatically learn complex patterns alleviates the burden of manual annotation, thereby reducing overall costs associated with sentiment analysis tasks.",
    "As shown in C2 community of Fig. 2, evident is the prevalence of deep learning methods surpassing traditional machine learning approaches in sentiment analysis.",
    "This C2 community stands out with its extensive network of nodes and connections, indicating the significance of deep learning in the sentiment analysis domain.",
    "Notably, keywords from other sub-communities exhibit strong ties to those within the prominent C2 community."
  ]
}